QuestData.Title: WANTED: Commander Sarj'eth
QuestData.Description: Wanted for attacks against the Alliance!$b$bCommander Sarj'eth is responsible for leading several raids and ambushes against our soldiers.$b$bLast seen near the vicinity of this command poster.$b$bExtreme caution advised!$b$bUpon completion of the mission, report to Lieutenant Hawkins for commendation.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve the head of Commander Sarj'eth.
